title: Daily Wire Backstage: Biden’s Congressional Address
description:
Will Biden be able to make it to the end of this speech without taking a nap? If he manages to make it all the way through without a single "C'mon, man,” how can we be sure it wasn’t faked like the moon landing? How many times could Kamala have visited the border between the start and finish of this crapshow?
Join this roundtable discussion featuring Ben Shapiro, Andrew Klavan, Matt Walsh, Michael Knowles, and Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing to find out!
